<br>
unbuffed my stats when doing battle with the EJ dragon:<br>
<br>
MR: 121<br>
PR: 132<br>
<br>
Then buffs (this dragon doesn't seem to dispell much if at all).<br>
<br>
MR: 161 ish (I forget the exact number)<br>
PR: 172 ish<br>
<br>
Then add potiions:<br>
<br>
MR: 209 or something like that<br>
PR: 200+ something<br>
<br>
Then add bard songs<br>
<br>
MR: 245 or so<br>
PR: 250 something<br>
<br>
<br>
So, off we go to kill a dragon.  I resisted all the Poison breath spells, no problem.  Didn't get poisoned once.   However, I spend a good portion of the battle feared.  Seemed only those with MR above 300 or so were able to resist the Dragon Fear spell.<br>
<br>
We lost the first and second battle with this beast.  The second battle we didn't have enough PR potions so the second go my PR was down to 180 or so and I still resisted all the poison breath spells.   So it seems that I could give up some PR gear for MR gear, the problem is, I can't seem to find much more MR gear a druid can use.<br>
<br>
Here is what I have MR wise:<br>
<br>
Sarnek Battle Shield and Mistmoore shield +10mr  was using MM shield it also has PR<br>
Tranix Crown +20<br>
2 Diamond rings +7 x2<br>
Bone Arms +5<br>
Thex Hammer (range slot) +5?  can't remember<br>
2 MR bracers +7 x2<br>
Some +5 all resists necklace from a werewolf<br>
Paw mask +5 mr I think<br>
Gnomish Enviroment suite.   MR?  dont' remember now,  PR though<br>
<br>
I think that's my whole list.   Sorry for the inaccuracies, I'm at work and doing this from memory.<br>
<br>
What else is there?   <p>-Trevize Skallagrim - 58th Preserver - Clan Skallagrim - Drinal
