<br>
Anything over that mark does nothing.  In fact, there use to be a bug that would actually wrap around your resistance numers after 255.<br>
<br>
Ex. = If your resistance number was 260, the server would read it as 5 (260-255=5).  I think they fixed the bug, though I'm pretty sure there is still a soft cap at 255.<br>
<br>
